# Up-Down Counter (IP Catalog)

## Overview
Implements an up-down counter using Vivado IP Integrator.

## Board
Arty A7 (Artix-7)

## Tools
- Xilinx Vivado (IP Integrator)

## Description
This project recreates the up-down counter using IP blocks instead of writing the full design in Verilog.

## Inputs
- Clock
- Reset
- Direction control

## Outputs
- LED output (counter value)

## Notes
Demonstrates usage of Vivado IP catalog and block design approach.
